[Teleport to Hunting Grounds]
You may teleport to any of the following hunting locations. Each teleport requires a sum of AA.
Pilgrim's Necropolis (30-40) - 13000 AA
Necropolis of Worship (40-50) - 5500 AA
The Saint's Necropolis (70-80) - 9600 AA

Catacomb of the Heretic (30-40) - 12000 AA
Catacomb of the Branded (40-50) - 13000 AA
